reviews.text: Food is very average for the price. Had a burger, but is was wet and loose. Customer service was ok.

Fair food for stop-by meals. Good to have a leisure meal there. 
Service is good.

Like they are now serving coffee in ceremic mug rather than disposable paper cups. However, the vegetable definitely unfresh like those i put the fridge for 3 days.....it all turned brown on the edges.
The coffee is good and inexpensive, it could be warmer at times. The breakfast is delicious, though the amount of food could be greater. They offer upgrades to the breakfast though.

Egg Benedict - lots of water came out when I stick my knife onto the egg, got a weird sour taste to it too. Had sore tummy afterwards. Other food on the place were oily and lukewarm, tastes terrible as well. Coffee is sub-par. Squashy tables, steep price. Dont why there are still so many customers.

reviews.text:
It's a neighborhood mall. Has shops supply to the needs of the residents of Cityone. There's a MacD, Starbucks, Manning's, Watson's, and numerous restaurants. Nothing fancy. 

The one shop worth mentioning though, is the Adidas Outlet. This shop has a good selection of the previous season's collection at bargain prices. Just this shop alone is worth visiting this mall.
Not a big shopping centre. Nevertheless, some eateries still attract students and visitors.
A good mall with a good balance between fashion and other stuff for people who don't buy clothing every day.
Good.👍
A good place for the local community with real products useful for the locals.

reviews.text:
It's a neighborhood mall. Has shops supply to the needs of the residents of Cityone. There's a MacD, Starbucks, Manning's, Watson's, and numerous restaurants. Nothing fancy. 

The one shop worth mentioning though, is the Adidas Outlet. This shop has a good selection of the previous season's collection at bargain prices. Just this shop alone is worth visiting this mall.
商場店舖種類各式各樣，尤其食館特別多！
沒有泊車優惠，可以不去。

為沙田最大型私人屋苑，"致富"與 "置富" 同音因而得名。第一城的交通真是方便。城內有兩個商塲; 置富第一城，及在銀城街的置富第一城.樂薈。置富第一城的商場有兩層，面積較大、樂薈商塲是地下那層，樓上是停車場。兩面商塲都夠光猛，食物店多元化，中西都有。置富第一城中心有一個廣場，也稱置富第一"園"，每當節日期間，"園"內就舉辦嘉年華活動(如中秋嘉年華、聖誕節)，共賀中秋，為第一城居民帶來節日氣氛、家家共享、快樂年年。

reviews.text: 價錢合宜不會太貴，而且又好食，高度推薦
烏蠅長期供候，客人嘈吵
閒時坐在大堂吃餐晚舒適的，室内光線柔和，設輕盈早餐唯奶茶咖啡要加費，也有特色飲料，服務很不錯。
主打all day breakfast嘅餐廳，仲有各式咖啡特飲同輕盈西餐，環境輕鬆舒適，可以坐著一整個下午
All day breakfast呢個價算幾抵食，味道份量都唔錯，係環境爭d，有d污蠅飛過，另外員工有返d笑容會更好
